<li class="commentbody highlighted" id="comment-709939">
			<cite><a href='http://smittenkitchen.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>deb</a></cite>
						&nbsp;
			<a class="commentlink" href="#comment-709939" title="">June 8, 2011</a> 

		
			<div class="commentcount">507</div>

				<p>Berry sinking has to do with the heaviness of the berries versus the thickness of the batter. Thicker batters and lighter berries sink less; thinner batters and heavier berries sink more.</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
