				<p>This is in the oven right now and I can&#8217;t wait for it to come out! For everyone who has trouble with the batter &#8211; adding cold eggs and milk to room temp butter will make it look as if it is curdled. I always try to take my eggs (and milk if needed) out of the fridge early so that they can warm up a little bit. I didn&#8217;t when making this cake today, and my batter still smoothed out and looked okay in the end.</p>
