Our friend asked for &#8220;Strawberry Cake&#8221; when it was birthday time.  As I googled around I was disappointed to see recipes calling for strawberry-flavored gelatin, oh please. Why I didn&#8217;t think to look here first&#8230;. anyway, thank you so much for what I&#8217;m sure will become a family favorite!</p>
